# ========== Project-only: push only what we work on, not the whole MQ2 instance ==========
# Tracks: lua/itemui, lua/scripttracker, lua/mq/ItemUtils.lua, Macros (sell/loot + config templates),
#        resources (ItemUI UI files), epic_quests, README, .cursor (except .cursor/agents).
# Ignores: config/, plugins/, docs/, .cursor/agents, archive_backups.ps1, etc.

# --- Root: ignore everything, then un-ignore only project paths ---
/*
!.gitignore
.cursor/*
.github/*
!README.md
!DEPLOY.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!release_manifest.json
!default_config_manifest.json
!patcher/
!epic_quests/
!config_templates/
!scripts/
!lua/
!Macros/
!resources/
!docs/

# --- Ignore these project paths (do not track or push) ---
.cursor/agents/

# --- docs: only track new user-facing documentation ---
docs/*
!docs/INSTALL.md
!docs/CONFIGURATION.md
!docs/DEVELOPER.md
!docs/TROUBLESHOOTING.md
!docs/RELEASE_AND_DEPLOYMENT.md
!docs/ARCHITECTURE.md

